{"tid":364553,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［齊來做個上進撚］成日話要返工學野 究竟點樣學、學啲咩？集思廣益","createTime":"2017-08-18T13:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T01:04:48.000Z","uid":12731,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a50cfecbd1f6c46736fc1864c6c1b9649f8a6cfd","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"成日聽到啲上進撚話要返工學野，fresh grad仲有好多trainee programme，我都有幸入咗一個trainee programme，但返咗幾星期，越來越唔知自己做緊乜。究竟有咩要學，同埋要點學呢？<br />\n<br />\n知識上，做野我會盡量嘗試接觸多啲範疇，但有時公司啲job真係好單一，而且感覺到個supervisor自己都做嚟做去果幾味，唔會比到咩新鮮野我做。呢個時候我應該去隔離team r野做？ 試下爭取sit老世開會？我搵本簿寫低自己每日學過乜，但越寫越少而且好凌亂，學到嘅野散修修咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而soft skill有啲長進。成日要打電話同唔同parties傾野，negotiate啲terms，一開始怕怕羞，口震震，依家唔打得都嚇得下人，同其他人夾野都似返個大人。不過同同事相處始終麻麻，成日口不擇言，用對同學朋友果套對senior同埋supervisor，驚俾人感覺串串貢，輕佻，但仲未改到，但總結呢幾星期我進步最大係soft skills.<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有野分享，或者指點下？真心賜教，同埋想討論呢樣野好耐，一直苦無機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：intern parttime返過幾份，但fulltime就啱啱開始返，所以無乜精闢獨到見解，純粹引起討論同埋學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eba36120f89afa5195573d800a9145718e8dbb5","tid":364553,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"學下點食女同事先la"},{"pid":"79f195bbd1b6f7cc89f7ff75f190245bdcf48cdd","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學下點食女同事先la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同同事相處都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好在圍內本身有啲同學同一間公司，無係自己team識新人都未至於無人一齊食lunch"},{"pid":"ec45422b240846242b638e6c627c4c835c02b6ad","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T13:55:14.000Z","msg":"無人有呢個疑問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f3b6c4676fdb6bed1ac0b65020447d463eb6f4","tid":364553,"uid":125646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人有呢個疑問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我而家翻intern都已經有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcc1feeb73709a6d204f34e5bc276db28cf45f1","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無人有呢個疑問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我而家翻intern都已經有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有無咩見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係返返下工好快就會死做爛做唔會再諗學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cb78c0726f76858008c238d9ba3dd363fa62d4","tid":364553,"uid":58353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:33:46.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n返緊intern 同某幾個同事叫做有計傾<br />\n但比manager 話我做野快手 但個人比較靜<br />\n其實係因為同隔離女同事無咩兩咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿尾三十頭個d 岩岩結婚無仔女，都唔知有咩好講<br />\n反而男同事會多野講d<br />\n但我都無理繼續自己做野 雖然都少少尷尬啦"},{"pid":"cfd7b13768fef0c490a56674805a8b78bd4753b4","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n返緊intern 同某幾個同事叫做有計傾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但比manager 話我做野快手</span> 但個人比較靜<br />\n其實係因為同隔離女同事無咩兩咀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿尾三十頭個d 岩岩結婚無仔女，都唔知有咩好講<br />\n反而男同事會多野講d<br />\n但我都無理繼續自己做野 雖然都少少尷尬啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前intern都做野好快手，但後來發現做咁快得益嘅唔會係自己，了解下自己做緊乜好過（當然又唔好hea住拖長嚟做）。但係就算諗完唔識/唔敢問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b91bd0ac5bd229160ab9b3094cbb0c9c8eaaa19","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54a5b69f6cf02cdf10d04e02d0e11bbf31497b96","tid":364553,"uid":125646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無人有呢個疑問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我而家翻intern都已經有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有無咩見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係返返下工好快就會死做爛做唔會再諗學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會拖長黎做，反正個manager自己又唔急，咁我咁認真做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c424f9ab853c4eace06555bd97ddb2642821291a","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無人有呢個疑問咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我而家翻intern都已經有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你有無咩見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係返返下工好快就會死做爛做唔會再諗學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會拖長黎做，反正個manager自己又唔急，咁我咁認真做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會認真，但唔係認真係快呢方面"},{"pid":"4e6d737e3b4b4f529019a5219b6f85ce84b323ae","tid":364553,"uid":133662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:00:48.000Z","msg":"覺得番工冇野學係因為自己唔鐘意份工 如果你鐘意就會自然想學多啲 唔會覺做既野悶 或者唔知為乜<br />\n<br />\n所以 應該轉工？"},{"pid":"4835a2e0dd0e3fd520ea021d4e63d501943dc5e5","tid":364553,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得番工冇野學係因為自己唔鐘意份工 如果你鐘意就會自然想學多啲 唔會覺做既野悶 或者唔知為乜<br />\n<br />\n所以 應該轉工？</blockquote><br />\n我想學啊但唔知點學<br />\n成日掛住問野唔做野又驚老世唔鍾意"},{"pid":"0b36c657e2ab11bd15feeb6d4a8a6e3b834fa31a","tid":364553,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:04:48.000Z","msg":"學同人溝通同相處技巧，仲有可以識多d fd 子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}